---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="positive-city"
    class="wheat-relative wheat-font-serif wheat-min-h-screen wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-py-12 wheat-py-24@md wheat-pos-city"
>
    <div class="wheat-container wheat-px-6">
        <div class="wheat-text-center wheat-mb-12">
            <span class="wheat-text-xs wheat-text-sm@md wheat-tracking-widest wheat-uppercase wheat-block wheat-mb-4 trigo-positive-chapter">
                La Ciudad
            </span>
            <h2 class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-text-5xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-pos-city-title wheat-mb-6">La Ciudad Refugio</h2>
            <p class="wheat-text-lg wheat-pos-city-desc wheat-max-w-2xl wheat-mx-auto">
                <ShareableQuote
                    quote="El trigo nos pidió quedarnos quietos. A cambio, nos dio muros."
                />
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="wheat-grid wheat-grid--cols-2 wheat-items-center wheat-gap-12">
            <div class="wheat-pos-city-features wheat-space-y-6">
                <div class="wheat-flex wheat-items-start wheat-gap-4 wheat-p-6 wheat-pos-city-feature wheat-rounded-lg wheat-border wheat-transition-colors wheat-group">
                    <div class="wheat-pos-city-feature-icon-wrapper wheat-rounded-full wheat-transition-colors">
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="wheat-pos-city-feature-icon"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="wheat-pos-city-feature-title wheat-text-lg wheat-font-bold wheat-mb-2">Jericó</h3>
                        <p class="wheat-pos-city-feature-desc wheat-text-sm">
                            8000 a.C. - La primera ciudad amurallada
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="wheat-flex wheat-items-start wheat-gap-4 wheat-p-6 wheat-pos-city-feature wheat-rounded-lg wheat-border wheat-transition-colors wheat-group">
                    <div class="wheat-pos-city-feature-icon-wrapper wheat-rounded-full wheat-transition-colors">
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="wheat-pos-city-feature-icon"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M3.75 21h16.5M4.5 3h15M5.25 3v18m13.5-18v18M9 6.75h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m3-6H15m-1.5 3H15m-1.5 3H15M9 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h3.75c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="wheat-pos-city-feature-title wheat-text-lg wheat-font-bold wheat-mb-2">Çatalhöyük</h3>
                        <p class="wheat-pos-city-feature-desc wheat-text-sm">
                            7500 a.C. - 10,000 habitantes conviviendo
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="wheat-flex wheat-items-start wheat-gap-4 wheat-p-6 wheat-pos-city-feature wheat-rounded-lg wheat-border wheat-transition-colors wheat-group">
                    <div class="wheat-pos-city-feature-icon-wrapper wheat-rounded-full wheat-transition-colors">
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="wheat-pos-city-feature-icon"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M12 21v-8.25M15.75 21v-8.25M8.25 21v-8.25M3 9l9-6 9 6m-1.5 12V10.332A48.36 48.36 0 0012 9.75c-2.551 0-5.056.2-7.5.582V21M3 21h18M12 6.75h.008v.008H12V6.75z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="wheat-pos-city-feature-title wheat-text-lg wheat-font-bold wheat-mb-2">Uruk</h3>
                        <p class="wheat-pos-city-feature-desc wheat-text-sm">4000 a.C. - La primera metrópolis</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="wheat-pos-city-text wheat-text-base wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-pt-4">
                    Por primera vez, el ser humano no estaba a merced de la tormenta o la bestia.
                    Creamos espacios controlados, templados y seguros. La "casa" dejó de ser un
                    concepto temporal para convertirse en un legado.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="wheat-relative wheat-pos-city-visual-col wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center">
                <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-pos-city-radial-glow"></div>

                <div class="wheat-relative wheat-pos-city-card-container">
                    <div class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-pos-city-blur-glow wheat-rounded-full"></div>

                    <div class="wheat-relative wheat-pos-city-arch-card wheat-rounded-2xl wheat-border wheat-p-8">
                        <div class="wheat-pos-city-block"></div>
                        <div class="wheat-pos-city-block wheat-pos-city-block--2"></div>
                        <div class="wheat-pos-city-block wheat-pos-city-block--3"></div>
                        <div class="wheat-pos-city-block wheat-pos-city-block--4"></div>

                        <div class="wheat-pos-city-block wheat-pos-city-block--large-1"></div>
                        <div class="wheat-pos-city-block wheat-pos-city-block--large-2"></div>

                        <div class="wheat-pos-city-temple">
                            <div class="wheat-pos-city-temple-glow"></div>
                            <div class="wheat-pos-city-temple-core">
                                <div class="wheat-pos-city-temple-light"></div>
                                <div class="wheat-pos-city-temple-label">Centro</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .wheat-pos-city {
        color: #e7e5e4;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-desc {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-feature {
        background-color: #1c1917;
        border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-feature:hover {
        border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-feature-icon-wrapper {
        width: 3rem;
        height: 3rem;
        background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-feature:hover .wheat-pos-city-feature-icon-wrapper {
        background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-feature-icon {
        width: 1.5rem;
        height: 1.5rem;
        color: #10b981;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-feature-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-feature-desc {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-text {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-visual-col {
        height: 500px;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-radial-glow {
        background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1), transparent, transparent);
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-card-container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 320px;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-blur-glow {
        background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05);
        filter: blur(40px);
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-arch-card {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        gap: 0.75rem;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #1c1917, #0c0a09);
        border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-block {
        height: 4rem;
        background: linear-gradient(to top, #292524, #1c1917);
        border-radius: 0.125rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-block--2 {
        height: 6rem;
        margin-top: -2rem;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-block--3 {
        height: 5rem;
        margin-top: -1rem;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-block--4 {
        height: 7rem;
        margin-top: -3rem;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-block--large-1 {
        height: 8rem;
        margin-top: -4rem;
        grid-column: span 2 / span 2;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-block--large-2 {
        height: 7rem;
        margin-top: -3rem;
        grid-column: span 2 / span 2;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-temple {
        height: 12rem;
        background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(6, 95, 70, 0.6), rgba(6, 95, 70, 0.4));
        border: 2px solid rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.4);
        border-radius: 0.125rem;
        margin-top: -8rem;
        grid-column: span 4 / span 4;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-temple-glow {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 120%, rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.2), transparent, transparent);
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-temple-core {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-temple-light {
        width: 0.75rem;
        height: 0.75rem;
        background-color: #34d399;
        border-radius: 50%;
        animation: pulse-light 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
        box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.5);
    }
    .wheat-pos-city-temple-label {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.8);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }
    @keyframes pulse-light {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.9); }
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-space-y-6 > * + * {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
    }
</style>
